            "title": "滬指開市升2點 深成指升7點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段靠穩，上證綜指以3378點開市，升2點或0.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10152點，亦升7點或0.08%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升3點或0.1%，開報3872點；創業板指數開市報2026點，升1點或0.08%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14985381-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%872%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%877%e9%bb%9e",
