        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指漲176點報23828點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段進一步向上，恒生指數開市報23828點，升174點或0.74%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5269點，升50點或0.97%；國企指數以8643點開市，升66點或0.78%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-web_09992-00019.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-web_09992-00019.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">個別股份方面，泡泡瑪特(09992)及順豐控股(06936)獲納入富時中國50指數，由6月20日起生效，兩股今早於競價時段均造好。泡泡瑪特開報249元，升1.22%；順豐控股開報42.9元，升0.23%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，多家公司趁市旺配股或供股集資，股價今早普遍受壓。科倫博泰(06990)開報359元，暫時無升跌；龍蟠科技(02465)開報6.4元，跌2.88%；濠暻科技(02440)開報2.14元，挫14.74%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：科倫博泰官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_06990-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：科倫博泰官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_06990-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：科倫博泰官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">續有藥業股公布新藥開發的消息，今早股價普遍造好。康方生物(09926)開報83.5元，升2.9%；和黃醫藥(00013)開報24.3元，升2.53%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14985364-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2176%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123828%e9%bb%9e",
